          <div class="breadcrumbs__main"><a class="breadcrumbs__main-pagename breadcrumbs__main-pagename--inactive" href="https://captainfoods.co.jp/stg/shop/">TOP</a>
            <div class="breadcrumbs__main-carret"><img src="/stg/cf2022/img\icons\icon-arrow-right-red.svg" alt=""></div><span class="breadcrumbs__main-pagename">お支払い方法・ポイントについて</span>
